net.corda.client.fxutils

Class ReadOnlyBackedObservableMapBase<K,A,B>

  • net.corda.client.fxutils.ReadOnlyBackedObservableMapBase<K,A,B>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - The key type.
    A - The exposed map element type.
    B - Auxiliary data subclasses may wish to store in the backing map.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AssociatedList, LeftOuterJoinedMap

    public class ReadOnlyBackedObservableMapBase<K,A,B>

    class ReadOnlyBackedObservableMapBase is a base class implementing all abstract functions required for an ObservableMap using a backing HashMap that subclasses should modify.

    Non-read-only API calls throw.

    See Also:
